-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Adidas, Ashtead Group, British American Tobacco  
-- 
-- Tue Jul 15, 2014 01:26AM EDT
-- None



July 15 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Adidas and Anglo Pacific, on Tuesday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Adidas <ADSGn.DE>: UBS, DZ Bank cut target price on the stock * Admiral <ADML.L>: Numis cuts to add from buy rating * Anglo Pacific <APF.L>: BMO starts with an outperform rating * Ashtead Group <AHT.L>: Berenberg starts with buy rating * British American Tobacco <BATS.L>: Nomura cuts price target to 3670p from 3700p Following is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Tuesday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.* Adidas <ADSGn.DE>: UBS cuts target price to 88 euros from 91 euros; rating buy  * Adidas <ADSGn.DE>: DZ Bank cuts target price to 88.00 eur from 90.00 eur; rating buy  * Admiral <ADML.L>: Numis cuts to add from buy rating * Aalberts <AALB.AS>: Berenberg raises target price to 27.80 euros from 27 euros; rating buy * Anglo Pacific <APF.L>: BMO starts with an outperform rating; 225p target price * Ashtead Group <AHT.L>: Berenberg starts with buy  * Ashtead Group <AHT.L>: Berenberg starts with target price 1110p  * Belgacom <BCOM.BR>: Barclays raises target price to 19 euros from 18 euros; underweight * British American Tobacco <BATS.L>: Nomura cuts price target to 3670p from 3700p;rating buy * Italcementi <ITAI.MI>: Berenberg cuts target price to 6.00 euros from 6.10 euros; sell * Kazakhmys <KAZ.L>: Nomura raises price target to 275p from 225p; rating reduce  * Kingfisher <KGF.L>: Jefferies cuts price target to 450p from 480p; rating buy * Millicom <MICsdb.ST>: Barclays raises target price to sek 610 from sek 600; equalweight * SEB <SEBa.ST>: SocGen raises target price to sek 100 from sek 95; rating buy * Suez Environnement <SEVI.PA>: Berenberg cuts target to 15.30 euros from 16.60 euros; buy